abstract: "Production-grade system for extracting structured financial data from SEC 10-K/10-Q/8-K filings using a QLoRA fine-tuned Llama 3.1 8B model with 4-bit quantization. Achieves 94% extraction accuracy with 77% memory reduction compared to FP32, enabling deployment on consumer GPUs."
